first_reading.text:
[[So 2,3]]Seek the LORD, all you humble of the earth, who have observed his law; Seek justice, seek humility; perhaps you may be sheltered on the day of the LORD'S anger.
[[So 3,12]]But I will leave as a remnant in your midst a people humble and lowly, Who shall take refuge in the name of the LORD;
[[So 3,13]]the remnant of Israel. They shall do no wrong and speak no lies; Nor shall there be found in their mouths a deceitful tongue; They shall pasture and couch their flocks with none to disturb them.
